	<Title>
		Quit smoking: Pick a quit day
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;If you&apos;re thinking about quitting, go ahead and pick a specific day to quit, called your quit day. Don&apos;t set your quit day too far in the future or you may find it hard to follow through. Pick a specific day within the next month to quit smoking. But don&apos;t do it before you have a quit-smoking plan in place. Pick a random day as your quit day or pick a day that holds special meaning for you. Just pick a quit day and then stick to it.&lt;/p&gt;
	</Body>
